sub_title: Best Seller Author “Dijitalin Kitabı Mı Olur?” | Brand Strategy & Digital Marketing Cons.| Mentor at Google | Keynote Speaker
summary:
After concluding her Business Management and MBA studies, Göksemin Gökalp Özdemir has managed various international brands such as Calvin Klein, Swatch, G-Star Raw, Vakko and many others throughout her career.
 
She has played a major role in the growth phase of more than 900+ startups and entrepreneurs. Besides giving consultancy on business management, branding and digital marketing, she is also mentoring entrepreneurs in well-known startup programs such as Google Launchpad, Isbank Workup, Seedstars, BBVA Momentum, Cherie Blair Foundation, WeWork Labs, StartupBootCamp and Bayer Grants4Apps.
 
Additionally, she is giving lectures at Turkey's top universities, and private companies on branding, business management and digital marketing.
